          h3 Accordion
          p
            | By default child menu items are always visible. To apply the accordion effect, just add the
            code data-nav
            | attribute to the main
            code= "<ul>"
            | . When clicking on a parent item, an open one will close, allowing only one open nested list at a time. To avoid this behavior, just append
            code {multiple:true}
            | to the data attribute.
          h3.tm-article-subtitle Example
          .grid(data-grid-margin='')
            .width-medium-1-2
              p
                code data-nav
              ul.nav.nav-side.nav-parent-icon.width-medium-2-3(data-nav='')
                li.active
                  a(href='') Active
                li
                  a(href='') Item
                li.parent
                  a(href='#') Parent
                  div(style='overflow: hidden; height: 0; position: relative;')
                    ul.nav-sub
